Would it be difficult to add more levels?
Here are the current levels:
```
        LEVEL_1(1, R.style.LevelOne, 5, 20, 85),
        LEVEL_2(2, R.style.LevelTwo, 10, 30, 86),
        LEVEL_3(3, R.style.LevelThree, 15,40, 87),
